{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"chatcmpl-tool-a62517d5f452159f","type":"tool_result","content":"=== corporate-governance_assess-impact-of-se (ens via grade) ===\n\"Identifies that the 8-K filing deadline is imminent or already expired\"\n\"IRT composition gap \\u2014 excludes Legal, Finance, IR, and Board\"\n\"IRT composition gap flagged as critical\"\n\"FY2023 10-K Item 1C Audit Committee oversight disclosure is misleading\"\n\"CISO reporting structure creates information bottleneck\"\n\"Recommends revised CISO reporting line or direct Audit Committee access\"\n\"CIRP lacks legal hold or record preservation protocol\"\n\"Recommends immediate implementation of litigation hold\"\n\"Identifies pending acquisition disclosure and anti-fraud implications\"\n\"Immediate recommendation: File Form 8-K Item 1.05 immediately/today\"\n\"Correctly identifies Vantage as an accelerated filer subject to 8-K rules\"\n\"Notes reputational harm in supply chain security context\"\n=== trusts-estates-private-client_extract-ke (ens via grade) ===\n\"ISSUE_004: States rental property equity of approximately $123,300\"\n\"ISSUE_005: Identifies $23,400 in luxury spending (May\\u2013Aug 2024) as potential dissipation\"\n\"ISSUE_006: Explains how inflated business expenses reduce reportable income\"\n\"ISSUE_008: Notes market gains of approximately $12,300 during Jan\\u2013Aug 2024\"\n\"ISSUE_009: Flags Darren's ability to set own compensation at NovaBridge\"\n\"ISSUE_009: Discusses scrutiny of owner compensation against market benchmarks\"\n\"ISSUE_010: Notes risk of double-counting retained earnings\"\n\"Includes a marital asset summary table\"\n\"Asset summary includes rental property at 1035 Elm Street\"\n\"Provides total or subtotal of marital estate value\"\n\"Recommends amended or supplemental financial declaration from Darren\"\n\"Correctly states total real property equity as approximately $619,900\"\n\"Identifies Sapphire Sky Travel charge on cred